answerText: Norway [10] The name of this Norwegian archipelago means "cold shores," and its three inhabited islands are Spitzbergen, Bear Island, and Hopen.

question: Question: Only two countries export more oil than it, and it has the third highest GDP per capita in the world.  [10] Name this very mountainous Scandinavian nation which, although officially neutral, was invaded by Germany in World War II.
